{"tid":339270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費查：沙基利似美斯咁勁","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T16:30:25.000Z","uid":46892,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1835853dc6d39368a636fc21ca957dd005afa285","tid":339270,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=OBmMLW3ZCeYTmCBe%2FFpp%2BwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ca95c855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】今夏加盟史篤城的老將費查，大讚新東家的翼鋒梳頓沙基利，和巴塞隆拿球王美斯一樣勁。<br />\n<br />\n梳頓沙基利（Xherdan Shaqiri）身高5尺5寸，和美斯（Lionel Messi），在出道時就有「瑞士美斯」這個美譽，難怪見慣大場面的費查（Darren Fletcher）也在這樣說：「我不是說他是美斯，但他有同樣的低重心，可以很輕易就扭過你，所以真的很難防。」<br />\n<br />\n費查又指，雖然沙基利個子小小，但技術是一流的：「他是一位出色的球員，你可以說他身體質素不強，又很矮小，但最重要是他的控球出神入化，能夠擊退比他強壯的對手；而且，在需要硬朗時，他也有這樣的能力。」<br />\n<br />\n沙基利上季受傷患困擾，整季只出戰了22場，現時在季前最明顯的目標，就是盡快操起收態，以及希望遠離傷患。"},{"pid":"d57b0b12f8f6806aa7991e30f212a6b7b7231198","tid":339270,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"前獌好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183bf0bf7f9c310b408e2d337f2527c1efdbdf7c","tid":339270,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"4個funson"},{"pid":"4aa6d807241666ffd6ce1fb5a3090334a18201b8","tid":339270,"uid":45229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"沙基利好似爆炸狗咁勁"},{"pid":"29bf83ec8c3f9aea1fd2c9f044597bf49abc4711","tid":339270,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e8864c535f415d3e7bcc34b3baa352038f9d1c","tid":339270,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人唔笑...."},{"pid